  "page_help": "Urai Purakai & Kelvikkal",
  "help_system_title": "📋 Ohun Elai",
  "help_system_desc1": "FastWrite Ohun Pariya Attiruppukka Data Viluppukka Neyta (Billu, Nilakkuzhi, Anam) AI Udaya. Ni Anu Malai Thaanai Seyyum — Data Etaiyum Villai, Attiruppukka Ayyan Illai.",
  "help_system_desc2": "Seivai: PDF Kalitravan Seivum Kalam Onru Illada Palaiya Billu. Ohun Anu Ek Ek Billi Karippu, Katikai Theri, Pattai Patta, Data Attiruppukka (Billu Katikai, Natai, Neram, Viluvai Puri, Mukkum). Mukundai CSV Illada Excel Karlukkika.",
  "help_workflow_title": "🔄 Viruppu — Puthi Tharuvai",
  "help_step1_title": "API Katikai Suvarkkam",
  "help_step1_desc": "Pattikal → API Katikai Kil Lo Ki Ni AI Katikai Tarika (Thavam Google Gemini). Vedikka — Ohun Ni Katikai Kotukkum Illa. Ni AI Katikai Ivvai.",
  "help_step2_title": "Toli Attiruppukkal Kalitravan",
  "help_step2_desc": "Kalitravan & Karukkikal Kil Lo. PDF Fail Muttukka Illada Irukkuka (200 Billu Atkkovalai) Ki \"Toli Attiruppikka\" Tarika. Ohun Anu Ek Ek Billi Ki Katikai Arintha.",
  "help_step3_title": "Pattal Tharuva",
  "help_step3_desc": "Toli Attiruppukkal Ihunappu Onru Illada Palaiya Irukkuka Ki \"Pattal\" Tarika. Ni Billi Kal Kathamai Ki Pattal Form Vavattai Kaattukkum. Data Attiruppukka Ilai Tharuva (Billu Katikai, Natai, Neram, Viluvai) Ki Puri. Illada Pattal Ihu → + Puthia Pattal Tarika.",
  "help_step4_title": "Data Attiruppukka (Pannitta)",
  "help_step4_desc": "Toli Attiruppukkal Ihunappu Palaiya Irukkuka Ki \"Pannitta\" Tarika. Ohun AI Lo Billi Pattai Data Attiruppikka. Phali Toli Attiruppukkal Tolai Kattukum.",
  "help_step5_title": "Nokka & Anumati",
  "help_step5_desc": "Toli Attiruppukkal Ihunappu Palaiya Irukkuka Ki \"Anumati\" Tarika. Ni Billi Kal Kathamai Ki Attiruppukka Data Vavattai Kaattukkum. Ulla Samuttar Ki \"Billi Anumati\" Tarika. Vakkai Velai Nokka Thozhil Viluvai Ilan Marai.",
  "help_step6_title": "Fail Karukkikal",
  "help_step6_desc": "Toli Anumati Sekka Munpu Toli Attiruppukkal Ihu Pada. Anumati Toli Irukkuka Ki \"CSV\", \"XLSX\" Illada \"Viluvai Attukkum XLSX\" Tarika Karukkikal. Irukkuka Illa Anumati Koatpan Toli Karukkikka.",
  "help_tip_title": "💡 Anumati",
  "help_tip_text": "Solrai Tholai: Kalitravan → Pattal → Pannitta → Anumati → Karukkikal. Billi Irukkal (Thavam DEI, COSMOTE, VODAFONE) Pattal Tharuva Munpu Pannitta Attal Thalai. Pattal Tharunthaal Ohun Puthia Billi Anu Katikai Katikai.",
